quran[9{c,v,t}:
6,82,"haqeeqat mein to aman unhi ke liye hai aur raah raast par wohi hain jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne apne imaan ko zulm ke sath aaloda nahi kya """
6,83,yeh thi hamari woh Hujjat jo hum ne ibrahim ko is ki qoum ke muqaabla mein ataa ki hum jisay chahtay hain buland martabay ataa karte hain haq yeh hai ke tumhara rab nihayat Dana aur Aleem hai
6,84,"phir hum ne ibrahim ko ishaq aur yaqoob jaisi aulaad di aur har aik ko raah raast dikhayi ( wohi raah raast jo ) is se pehlay Nooh ko dikhayi thi aur usi ki nasal se hum ne DAWOD, sulaiman, ayub, yousuf, moose aur haroon ko ( hadaayat bakhsh ) iss terhan hum naiko karon ko un ki neki ka badla dete hain"
6,85,"( usi ki aulaad se ) Zikria, yahya, eesa aur ilyas ko ( raah yab kya ) har aik un mein se Saleh tha"
6,86,"( isi ke khandan se ) Ismael,Yasa'a , aur Younis aur loot ko ( rasta dekhaya ) inn mein se har aik ko hum ne tamam duniya walon par fazeelat ataa ki"
6,87,"neez un ke aaba o ajdaad aur un ki aulaad aur un ke bhai bundon mein se bahuton ko hum ne nawaza, inhen apni khidmat ke liye chunn liya aur seedhay rastay ki taraf unn ki rahnumai ki"
6,88,yeh Allah ki hadaayat hai jis ke sath woh apne bundon mein se jis ki chahta hai rahnumai karta hai lekin agar kahin un logon ne shirk kya hota to un ka sab kya karaya ghaarat ho jata
6,89,woh log thay jin ko hum ne kitaab aur hukum aur nabuwat ataa ki thi ab agar yeh log is ko maan-ne se inkaar karte hain to ( parwa nahi ) hum ne kuch aur logon ko yeh Nemat saump di hai jo is se munkir nahi hain
6,90,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! wohi log Allah ki taraf se hadaayat Yafta thay, unhi ke rasta par tum chalo, aur keh do ke mein ( is tableegh o hadaayat ke ) kaam par tum se kisi ajar ka taalib nahi hon, yeh to aik aam nasiyaat hai tamam duniya walon ke liye"
